  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 73-35-17, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REDUCE THE PENALTY FOR A PERSON LICENSED AS A REAL ESTATE BROKER WHO DOES NOT PAY THE LICENSE RENEWAL FEE WHEN IT BECOMES DUE FROM ONE HUNDRED PERCENT OF THE RENEWAL FEE TO FIFTY PERCENT OF THE RENEWAL FEE; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 73-35-7 AND 73-35-18, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, FOR THE PURPOSE OF POSSIBLE AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
